Amulet
You will need this to find out where the young Joon teleported to. The ruins of the mansion belonging to the scientist are located north of the city.
#subobj  1
Find the ruins of the mansion
The mansion's ruins are located north of the city. You can reach them through the gates in the southern  wall. But remember that after the mysterious developments in the mansion all approaches to it are guarded very well.
#subobj  2
Search the ruins
The pieces of the amulet used by the young Joon must be somewhere around here.
#subobj  3
Search the coffer
Mayhap, while they conducted the investigation,  they put everything connected with the events in the mansion into this coffer. You should have a good look at its contents.
